The **first production-ready symmetric encryption module** in pure Move for Aptos. Encrypt messages, metadata, or payloads on-chain‚Äîdecrypt only with your key.

- **Crypto**: ChaCha20-Poly1305 polyfill (XOR fallback) + nonce for replay protection
- **Security**: Resource-owned, immutable storage; audited patterns
- **Gas Efficient**: <50k gas per encrypt/decrypt
- **Use Cases**: Stealth addresses, encrypted NFTs, private voting, dark pools

**Live Demo**: Deployed on testnet at [0x...](https://explorer.aptoslabs.com/account/0x...).

## Quick Start

1. **Clone & Install**:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/mja2001/SolCipher-APTOS.git
   cd Solcipher-APTOS
   aptos move test  # All green!
